PerformanceResourceTimingFirstInterimRes.summary: The firstInterimResponseStart read-only property returns a immediately after the browser receives the first byte of the interim 1xx response (for example, 100 Continue or 103 Early Hints) from the server.

remarks.para: There is no end property for firstInterimResponseStart.
